Energetics. Compute the total energy output by AGN in the sample. 
Convert it into kinetic, thermal , radiative energy, quantify if the average n_e profile's excursion form the NFW can be achieved with this energy input over a the age of the universe.
Look into hydrodynamical simulations to convert a total energy input into a net displacement on the gas profile.
